OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,FThe independent body which oversees
OL,7,Fhealth care on the Isle of Man has
OL,8,Fannounced a series of urgent measures
OL,9,Fto address serious financial pressures
OL,10,Fon the service.
OL,12,FManx Care says its facing a projected
OL,13,F#15 million overspend and has revealed
OL,14,Fcost-cutting measures that include a
OL,15,Ftemporary suspension of elective
OL,16,Foperations, closing in-patient wards
OL,17,Fand a recruitment freeze.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
