OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,FIt comes days after doctors on the
OL,7,Fisland accepted an 8% pay offer,
OL,8,Fending a long-running dispute, and
OL,9,Faverting what would have been the
OL,10,Ffirst doctors' strike in its history.
OL,12,FBut the health body has stressed
OL,13,F"these actions are not being taken in
OL,14,Fresponse to the recently announced
OL,15,Fsettlement of the pay dispute with the
OL,16,FBritish Medical Association (BMA)".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
