OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,FIt says despite measures put in place
OL,7,Fin October 2024 to cut back on a
OL,8,Fprojected overspend to the tune of #10
OL,9,Fmillion in 2024 - 2025, expenditure
OL,10,Flevels are continuing to rise, pushing
OL,11,Fthe expected deficit to #15 million by
OL,12,Fthe end of the financial year.
OL,14,FIt adds that the new measures were
OL,15,Fagreed by the Manx Care Board in early
OL,16,FJanuary, and that, "subsequently we
OL,17,Fhave been working on the
OL,18,Fimplementation plans and discussing
OL,19,Fthe details of these actions with the
OL,20,FDHSC prior to formal announcement."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
