OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,FThe healthcare provider says new
OL,7,Ffunding agreed by Treasury means these
OL,8,Fplanned actions can now be reduced,
OL,9,Fbut some efficiencies will still be
OL,10,Fneeded during February and March.
OL,12,FFor patients receiving treatment off
OL,13,FIsland, this means a pause to non-
OL,14,Furgent procedures in Liverpool and
OL,15,FManchester until 31 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
