OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,FExcluded from this request are
OL,7,Fpatients awaiting cancer or clinically
OL,8,Furgent intervention, as well as those
OL,9,Fundergoing a course of treatment where
OL,10,Fany delay will impact on clinical
OL,11,Foutcomes.
OL,13,FOn-Island, the additional funding will
OL,14,Fenable many appointments to go ahead
OL,15,Fover the next two months, while those
OL,16,Fwho do have their appointment
OL,17,Fdisrupted will have them rearranged as
OL,18,Fearly as possible from April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
