OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,FManx Care says these measures will
OL,7,F"ensure the long-term sustainability"
OL,8,Fof its services, enable full clinical
OL,9,Fvalidation of waiting lists and reduce
OL,10,Fits reliance on additional or
OL,11,Ftemporary workforce.
OL,13,FIn a statement Manx Care said: "Our
OL,14,Fpriority continues to be maintaining
OL,15,Fthe safety of our services to the
OL,16,FIsland's population, responding to the
OL,17,Furgent and emergency needs of our
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
