OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,F"These measures further focus on
OL,7,Foptimising resources, controlling
OL,8,Fcosts, and improving financial
OL,9,Fgovernance while maintaining our core
OL,10,Fcommitment to patient safety and
OL,11,Fessential services.
OL,13,F"Our patients and service users are
OL,14,Fcentral to all our actions and
OL,15,Fdecisions as we navigate these
OL,16,Fnecessary changes."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
