OL,3,CManx Care forecasts #15m overspend
OL,4,Cwith cost-cutting measures announced
OL,6,FManx Care added that the decisions
OL,7,F"have not been made lightly" and that
OL,8,Fit understand the difficulties these
OL,9,Fchanges will bring for the community
OL,10,Fand its workforce, with potential
OL,11,Fimpact on waiting lists.
OL,13,FBut it also says that its committed to
OL,14,Fminimising disruption wherever
OL,15,Fpossible, adding that ensuring the
OL,16,Fsustainability of services within
OL,17,Fcosts is vital.
